},{"w":"dreams.","s":176.48,"e":178.54,"line":42},{"w":"If","s":188.34,"e":188.86,"line":43},{"w":"mercy","s":188.86,"e":189.34,"line":43},{"w":"is","s":189.34,"e":190.5,"line":43},{"w":"real,","s":190.5,"e":190.98,"line":43},{"w":"it","s":192.28,"e":192.8,"line":44},{"w":"reaches","s":192.8,"e":193.08,"line":44},{"w":"the","s":193.08,"e":193.62,"line":44},{"w":"pit.","s":193.62,"e":193.92,"line":44},{"w":"If","s":194.92,"e":196.04,"line":45},{"w":"love","s":196.04,"e":196.74,"line":45},{"w":"is","s":196.74,"e":197.02,"line":45},{"w":"alive,","s":197.02,"e":198.72,"line":45},{"w":"it","s":200.26,"e":201.66,"line":46},{"w":"doesn’t","s":201.66,"e":201.86,"line":46},{"w":"quit.","s":202.06,"e":202.76,"line":46}],"lines":[{"s":12.28,"e":12.36,"text":"Yeah—"},{"s":12.3,"e":15.14,"text":"If mercy got a border,"},{"s":17.38,"e":22.26,"text":"then mercy ain’t complete."},{"s":43.4,"e":46.48,"text":"They heard about a beast down burning in the deep,"},{"s":46.84,"e":49.92,"text":"Then turned the page and went back to sleep."},{"s":49.92,"e":53.38,"text":"Horned in the smoke, chained in the flame,"},{"s":53.76,"e":56.84,"text":"Everybody pointing, nobody took blame."},{"s":56.76,"e":60.2,"text":"If one creature cries and the whole world knows,"},{"s":60.36,"e":63.58,"text":"What kind of garden lets that pain grow?"},{"s":63.58,"e":67.06,"text":"You can call him fallen, you can call him wrong,"},{"s":67.06,"e":70.44,"text":"But leaving pain forever is a cruel old song."},{"s":70.44,"e":72.8,"text":"No creature left in fire,"},{"s":73.62,"e":76.06,"text":"No soul beneath the stone."},{"s":77,"e":79.4,"text":"If love is getting higher,"},{"s":79.86,"e":83.4,"text":"Then nobody burns alone."},{"s":83.4,"e":86.52,"text":"The whole world heard the thunder,"},{"s":86.84,"e":89.82,"text":"The whole world closed the door."},{"s":90.6,"e":93.28,"text":"No creature left in fire—"},{"s":93.2,"e":97.44,"text":"Not one beast anymore."},{"s":98.74,"e":101.84,"text":"Justice without mercy turns cold in the hand,"},{"s":102.24,"e":105,"text":"Rules without love don’t heal the land."},{"s":105.5,"e":108.46,"text":"If heaven is holy and light is true,"},{"s":108.46,"e":111.7,"text":"Then compassion gotta reach the monster too."},{"s":111.7,"e":115.04,"text":"Not praising the darkness, not kissing the chain,"},{"s":115.04,"e":118.52,"text":"Just saying forever pain is still pain."},{"s":118.52,"e":122.32,"text":"If we want peace, then we better get brave,"},{"s":122.32,"e":126.48,"text":"Pull every lost thing out of the grave."},{"s":126.48,"e":128.28,"text":"Fair don’t fix it, fear don’t heal,"},{"s":128.28,"e":129.96,"text":"Love gets loud when the suffering’s real."},{"s":129.94,"e":131.64,"text":"If one stays burning while the choirs sing,"},{"s":131.64,"e":135.54,"text":"Then mercy still ain’t spread its wings."},{"s":135.54,"e":137.52,"text":"No creature left in fire,"},{"s":138.48,"e":141.16,"text":"No soul beneath the stone."},{"s":141.94,"e":144.6,"text":"If love is getting higher,"},{"s":145.12,"e":148.34,"text":"Then nobody burns alone."},{"s":148.48,"e":151.66,"text":"The whole world heard the thunder,"},{"s":151.94,"e":155,"text":"The whole world closed the door."},{"s":155.7,"e":158.4,"text":"No creature left in fire—"},{"s":158.32,"e":162.36,"text":"Not one beast anymore."},{"s":163.28,"e":166.28,"text":"Drag the chains out, cool the coal,"},{"s":167.06,"e":170.36,"text":"Wash the smoke from every soul."},{"s":170.36,"e":173.28,"text":"No more cages, no more screams,"},{"s":173.7,"e":178.54,"text":"No more nightmares sold as dreams."},{"s":188.34,"e":190.98,"text":"If mercy is real,"},{"s":192.28,"e":193.92,"text":"it reaches the pit."},{"s":194.92,"e":198.72,"text":"If love is alive,"},{"s":200.26,"e":202.76,"text":"it doesn’t quit."}],"duration":211.28,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.301Z","stats":{"whisperWords":340,"polishedWords":296,"matched":287,"matchRate":0.97}}